{
  "text": "Some statements are relevant for two learning styles and therefore contribute to both learning style preferences. The respondents scored each statement (in total 65 statements) on a five-point Likert scale: ranging from \"not applicable to me\" (1), \"average\" (3) to \"fully applicable to me\" [CITATION_1] .",
